metadata.name: Soul Guardians#1
metadata.description:
The "Soul Guardians" is a collaborative artwork created by two artists. In this piece, a young couple faces a malevolent force and various threats, but they are protected by vibrant guardians. The artwork combines digital painting and digital collage techniques to showcase a diverse and visually captivating composition. The "Soul Guardians" symbolizes unity, the power of friendship, and mutual support. May this artwork resonate with you and ignite your imagination.
Size : 4000 px * 3000 px
